    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>本游戏没有天选之子，只有一个被BUG卡进里世界的倒霉小家伙。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/c9c302754e31eec3bd85c3bd0a2998b2.poster.avif?t=1763022051\" width=1028 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/c9c302754e31eec3bd85c3bd0a2998b2.webm?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/c9c302754e31eec3bd85c3bd0a2998b2.mp4?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>我在哪，我是谁，我该干什么？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我是谁？</strong> - 一千个玩家眼中，自有一千个哈姆雷特，这是你需要在这个世界里破解的，最终极的一个谜题</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>我在哪？</strong> - 一个癫狂的数字地狱，数百个精神不正常的角色在此永生</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>干什么？ - </strong>捡光所有垃圾，干翻所有NPC，在管理员删除你之前，找到世界的真相——或者，成为真相</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/901a531d773100cf7b28ff4280a7769c.poster.avif?t=1763022051\" width=1028 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/901a531d773100cf7b28ff4280a7769c.webm?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/901a531d773100cf7b28ff4280a7769c.mp4?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>怎么玩？</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>癫狂世界</strong> - 探索数百张地图，享受地貌带来的精神分裂。史诗感？连西兰花都在思考存在主义</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>清版模拟器 </strong>- 资源不可再生，你的终极目标是清空世界——包括你自己</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>碎片叙事</strong> - 没有主线，满地碎片。所有NPC可杀可撩，反正你的选择终将归于虚无</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BD做减法 </strong>- 装备是天，装备=技能+被动+数值，你的注意力只需放在装备上</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>下料猛 </strong>- 痛恨重复。每场战斗、每寸土地、每首BGM都独一无二，保证每分钟都在“惊喜”中精神错乱</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/9685f33404b0f0396bfc6614a53007f3.poster.avif?t=1763022051\" width=1028 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/9685f33404b0f0396bfc6614a53007f3.webm?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/9685f33404b0f0396bfc6614a53007f3.mp4?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索，收集，养成，然后干翻一切！……或者被一切干翻</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>300+ 精神堪忧旅伴</strong> - 这里是308号精神病院……哦不，是308方旅人。入院嘉宾包括：因脑袋像屁股而自卑的西兰花、用骷髅身姿探讨存在主义的丧尸哲学家、以及坚决否认药水是偷来的哥布林匠</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>300+ 可“永久删除”的NPC -</strong> 对，我们又水了一条。但亲手把Bug从世界里删除，不爽吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>60+ 自带BGM的癫狂BOSS</strong> - 燃起来！在摇滚重金属的洗礼下，迎接专治各种不服的强力首领。检验你策略的不是数值，是你的脑洞有多大</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/f829f8dc2e6357041a12396235b13158.poster.avif?t=1763022051\" width=1028 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/f829f8dc2e6357041a12396235b13158.webm?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/f829f8dc2e6357041a12396235b13158.mp4?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1000+ 逆天装备</strong> - 装备就是天！你能用它们搭配出什么离谱的玩法？我们很好奇</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ 激活集体潜能的角色卡牌</strong> - 集齐它们，为全队提供永久增益。养成？没有上限，只有肝的尽头</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>300+ 塞满你播放列表的魔性曲目</strong> - 把那个闹鬼的“大棚迪厅”，变成只属于你的DJ房</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/00f5255f6fec5cf58acf36155dde6e0b.poster.avif?t=1763022051\" width=912 height=786 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157170/extras/00f5255f6fec5cf58acf36155dde6e0b.webm?t=1763022051\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>现在，按下【进入游戏】，然后——祝你好运</strong></h2>",
